channel.title: Looking for a development team
channel.description:
I am Caelum and I need YOUR help! to create a RSPS.
I don't favor those with 200 "rep" over those with 1 "rep", I am looking for grafic, 3D editor/creator, coding and people skills, or even those who push them selves to learn and do well tho aren't very good at the moment.
The name of the server hasn't been chosen yet (all the good one's are taken... hmm NismoScape sounds good? jokes...) , i hope you will help me choose one...
to apply post and include the folowing:
♦your age ♣your name ♠your ocupation/job ♥your coding expirience ☺your email (can be pmed for your privacy)
well go ahead?!!
